name: WHERE DO MISSING PEOPLE GO?
description:
THIS IS A GAME FOR SOMEONE'S BIRTHDAY, AND WAS MADE IN 2 WEEKS!

WHERE DO MISSING PEOPLE GO? is a short horror, adventure game being filmed in the shoes of Detective Johnathan. On the search for 3 missing kids, he finds more than he was willing to barter.

Made with Unity, from Upscaled Productions.
